Description: SRM Agent — FRPC Sync + Monitoring
 Unified agent for Simple Remote Manager (SRM). Combines FRP Client
 (frpc) with automatic config sync and system monitoring in a single
 binary. Supports Linux and Windows. Replaces srm-frpc-client and
 srm-monitor-agent packages.
